column2: What is the patient's identification number?
What is the name of the antipsychotic that the doctor told you to take each day?
How many pills of _________________ (name of antipsychotic) did the doctor tell you to take each day?
Over the month since last visit with me, on how many days did you NOT TAKE your _________________ (name of antipsychotic)?
Over the month since your last visit with me, how many days did you TAKE LESS THAN the prescribed number of pills of your _________________ (name of antipsychotic)?
